show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/vuUAVp
show.description: Riya, a kind-hearted young woman betrayed by her own family and thrust into a world of cruelty and deception. Just when all hope seems lost, fate brings her into the orbit of Aryan, a mysterious and powerful businessman with a buried past. As their paths collide, both love and vengeance ignite, setting off a chain of gripping events that will test every bond.
